{"tid":2142591,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］電腦入唔到window","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T16:21:53.000Z","uid":234960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"db31826388558ff37dec2584d6c39007e9b76aa1","tid":2142591,"uid":234960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"電腦開到機 入到bios <br />\n但正常開機就會卡住<br />\n再reboot 就會show 正在修復 但又係卡住修復唔到<br />\n請問有無人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前間唔中會咁 但reboot幾次就得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxDeQLr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxDeQLr.png&h=54b6e24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nep2fca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNep2fca.png&h=40c76da0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95e30c396880c6a38992fc3076361070522d98b3","tid":2142591,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"電腦傳心師<br />\n試下用win 10 usb boot起"},{"pid":"86edf2f6cdfb6aff2f9427884f1d7f93224a95fb","tid":2142591,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"check左hdd/ssd先"},{"pid":"614d4141ac8088b63c0afdd1cc5c0e69012d8f26","tid":2142591,"uid":234960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86edf2f6cdfb6aff2f9427884f1d7f93224a95fb","tid":2142591,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:32:08.000Z","msg":"check左hdd/ssd先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:41:31.000Z","msg":"請問可以點樣chk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10c15639f271ccf6563c8101fedfa5421d37b77","tid":2142591,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"614d4141ac8088b63c0afdd1cc5c0e69012d8f26","tid":2142591,"uid":234960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86edf2f6cdfb6