eplyTime":"2020-08-08T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"我之前都係呢個情況，拆 display 用內置 display, 拆 ram 用朋友借返嚟個條，拆ssd 用普通 hd 都係入唔到 windows <br />\n最後放棄，砌咗部新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇返巴打原來都係用 gigabytes 底板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我其實都想知部機出咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}